2014-10-03 Nicolas Normand <nnormand@justcodeit.org>
	* cppmt::Opts: can choose behavior when opening configuration file fails (report error, ignore error or direct exit).
	* cppmt::Opts: can choose option (long and short) names for help and version, as well as help strings.

